Title: What Do I Call You?
Description:
Guardian! Or... teacher! Parent?

I want you to tell me what to call you. The other dryads will ask me who my druid is now that I am working in the garden on my own.

I want to tell them that I do not have a druid. I have you!

Tell me what title you prefer.
ObjectivesText: Speak with Dionaessa to choose a title in the Root-Bound Sanctuary.
